Description: 
Sharp World Clock 8.1.3.0 
If you love or just need to keep track of the world time, then you can download Sharp World Clock from our site, do not forget to go to the full news for this. Please note that you can add an unlimited number of hours, build them can be both in line and in the table. The clock itself can have different external views, for this you will have all the necessary settings, yet you can switch between the types of clocks, you can choose digital or conventional classic with the dial. 
Sharp World Clock shows next to the time the flag of the country, which is directly related to the clock, the size of the clock itself can also be changed, exposing their size from small to large, to whom it is convenient. You can always view the full list of cities in this or that country of the world, if for some reason there is no city in the list, you can add your own, do not forget to just specify all the necessary parameters. Sharp World Clock provides a large list of different types of time and date formats, for each clock you can individually adjust this parameter. You can open the world map and directly view the time zones on it, see where it is now, and where the night is, calculate the lunar phases and other other goodies. 

Developer: Johannes Wallroth
